msgid "TE-CL"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/vuln/httpSmuggling.rst:74
msgid ""
"TE-CL指前端服务器处理 ``Transfer-Encoding`` 请求头，而后端服务器处理 ``Content-Length`` "
"请求头。例如："
